  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK532">
<l>poccāppuk kollum pukaḻai yaṟiviṉai </l>
<l>nicca nirappukkoṉ ṟāṅku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Forgetfulness will destroy fame, even as constant poverty destroys knowledge.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
